snippet.title: Alter Aeon Class-Themed Advertisement
snippet.description:
Alter Aeon is a free fantasy text game that is fun for all ages!  Play now at http://alteraeon.com

This is the video version of our class-themed audio ad created for internet radio.  Please share it with all of your friends!

Download: http://lawful-evil.org/audio/alter_aeon_class_radio_ad_final.ogg
